<section id="register" class="py-16 bg-primary">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-white">立即報名</h2>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mwpedjgn" method="POST" class="space-y-6 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div>
          <label for="name" class="block text-gray-700 font-medium mb-2">姓名</label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="name"
            name="name"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent text-gray-700"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="email" class="block text-gray-700 font-medium mb-2">電郵地址</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent text-gray-700"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="phone" class="block text-gray-700 font-medium mb-2">WhatsApp 電話</label>
          <input
            type="tel"
            id="phone"
            name="phone"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent text-gray-700"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <input
            type="checkbox"
            id="newsletter"
            name="newsletter"
            class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 text-primary focus:ring-primary border-gray-300 rounded"
          />
          <label for="newsletter" class="ml-2 block text-gray-700">
            訂閱電子報，獲取最新AI課程資訊
          </label>
        </div>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full bg-secondary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
        >
          提交報名
        </button>
      </form>
      <div class="mt-12 text-sm text-white opacity-80 text-center">
        <p>⚡️ 重要提醒</p>
        <p>請自備手提電腦：課程包含大量實機操作練習，需要使用個人電腦進行學習。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>